155
00:08:58,844 --> 00:09:00,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Come on, Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

156
00:09:00,714 --> 00:09:04,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm looking forward to seeing</i>
<i>who gets out of the car.</i></b></font>

157
00:09:04,024 --> 00:09:07,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's been a while since I've been so excited.</i></b></font>

158
00:09:07,354 --> 00:09:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's kept us waiting for so long...</i></b></font>

159
00:09:09,654 --> 00:09:11,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But such an obvious</i>
<i>strategy won't work on me.</i></b></font>

160
00:09:11,794 --> 00:09:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll be watching you very closely.</i></b></font>

161
00:09:17,964 --> 00:09:19,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here it comes!</b></font>

162
00:09:19,464 --> 00:09:23,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Give him a path! Show him to the starting line!</b></font>

163
00:09:32,514 --> 00:09:34,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that car?</b></font>

164
00:09:34,154 --> 00:09:36,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone was waiting for that car.</b></font>

165
00:09:36,484 --> 00:09:38,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it's an Eight-Six.</b></font>

166
00:09:38,354 --> 00:09:43,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap! Where did all these people come from?!</b></font>

167
00:09:58,944 --> 00:10:00,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

168
00:10:00,174 --> 00:10:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me...!</b></font>

169
00:10:02,174 --> 00:10:05,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, the Eight-Six! Is it...?!</b></font>

170
00:10:11,454 --> 00:10:13,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

171
00:10:13,224 --> 00:10:15,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! It's him!</b></font>

172
00:10:27,704 --> 00:10:29,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So this is the guy...</b></font>

173
00:10:42,254 --> 00:10:44,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

174
00:10:44,924 --> 00:10:46,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?!</b></font>

175
00:10:46,124 --> 00:10:47,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened to your father?!</b></font>

176
00:10:47,394 --> 00:10:50,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My father told me to show up.</b></font>

177
00:10:50,324 --> 00:10:54,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if the car is here, without
your father, what good is it?</b></font>

178
00:10:54,394 --> 00:10:55,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

179
00:10:55,664 --> 00:10:57,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you going to do, Iketani?</b></font>

180
00:10:57,404 --> 00:11:00,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--This isn't... what you said...
--Because you said... we're all right...</b></font>

181
00:11:00,004 --> 00:11:02,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--I knew I shouldn't have come.</i>
--Kenji has to race after all...!</b></font>

182
00:11:02,704 --> 00:11:06,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn my old man! He really irritates me!</i></b></font>

183
00:11:06,074 --> 00:11:09,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Didn't your father say anything else?!</b></font>

184
00:11:09,574 --> 00:11:11,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He just told me...</b></font>

185
00:11:11,944 --> 00:11:16,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...to beat the FD on Akina's downhill.</b></font>

186
00:11:16,214 --> 00:11:17,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

187
00:11:17,354 --> 00:11:21,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did he tell you to drive?</b></font>

188
00:11:21,054 --> 00:11:22,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes...</b></font>

189
00:11:22,554 --> 00:11:25,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you beat...</b></font>

190
00:11:25,224 --> 00:11:28,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Keisuke Takahashi?</b></font>

191
00:11:28,034 --> 00:11:32,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I can't be sure until we really race...</b></font>

192
00:11:32,764 --> 00:11:35,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've beaten him before...</b></font>

193
00:11:35,374 --> 00:11:37,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You won once before...?!</b></font>

194
00:11:37,574 --> 00:11:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A full tank of gas is riding on this race...</b></font>

195
00:11:40,714 --> 00:11:43,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so if you let me, I'll win no matter what.</b></font>

196
00:11:47,614 --> 00:11:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me... Excuse me...</b></font>

197
00:11:50,954 --> 00:11:54,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! You idiot!</b></font>

198
00:11:54,554 --> 00:11:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch! What are you doing?!</b></font>

199
00:11:57,294 --> 00:12:00,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Just how stupid are you?!</b></font>

200
00:12:00,494 --> 00:12:04,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so embarrassed watching
you that I'm blushing!</b></font>

201
00:12:04,404 --> 00:12:05,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Move your car right now!</b></font>

202
00:12:05,904 --> 00:12:08,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't interfere with the race!</b></font>

203
00:12:08,104 --> 00:12:09,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get in that Eight-Six now!</b></font>

204
00:12:09,934 --> 00:12:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute, Itsuki.</b></font>

205
00:12:12,504 --> 00:12:14,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani! I'm so sorry!</b></font>

206
00:12:14,414 --> 00:12:18,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He is so stupid that he
doesn't understand anything.</b></font>

207
00:12:18,884 --> 00:12:21,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please forgive him!</b></font>

208
00:12:21,384 --> 00:12:24,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi... Do you, by any chance,</b></font>

209
00:12:24,784 --> 00:12:28,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>also deliver tofu, along with your father?</b></font>

210
00:12:28,094 --> 00:12:31,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I do all of the deliveries.
For the past five years.</b></font>

211
00:12:31,594 --> 00:12:33,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For the past five years?</b></font>

212
00:12:37,094 --> 00:12:40,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I understand. Takumi!</b></font>

213
00:12:40,704 --> 00:12:44,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right. I'll put you in
charge of the downhill race.</b></font>

214
00:12:44,274 --> 00:12:46,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about, Iketani?!</b></font>

215
00:12:46,274 --> 00:12:49,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If a novice like Takumi
tries the Akina downhill,</b></font>

216
00:12:49,474 --> 00:12:52,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>within minutes he'll cause
an accident and he'll die!</b></font>

217
00:12:52,044 --> 00:12:55,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about it. You need
to step aside and just watch.</b></font>

218
00:13:00,124 --> 00:13:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks for coming, Takumi.</b></font>

219
00:13:02,654 --> 00:13:04,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm counting on you.</b></font>

220
00:13:04,054 --> 00:13:06,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

221
00:13:06,324 --> 00:13:08,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry that we kept you waiting.</b></font>

222
00:13:08,534 --> 00:13:11,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really! I'm tired of waiting!</b></font>

223
00:13:14,704 --> 00:13:17,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're pretty young...</b></font>

224
00:13:17,204 --> 00:13:18,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's your name?</b></font>

225
00:13:18,674 --> 00:13:20,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi Fujiwara.</b></font>

226
00:13:20,504 --> 00:13:22,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll remember your name.</b></font>

227
00:13:22,414 --> 00:13:24,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Keisuke Takahashi.</b></font>

228
00:13:24,344 --> 00:13:27,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't make the same mistake twice.</b></font>

229
00:13:32,854 --> 00:13:35,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it really all right?</b></font>

230
00:13:35,054 --> 00:13:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's totally foolish to race
an Eight-Six against a FD.</b></font>

231
00:13:37,594 --> 00:13:39,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a huge difference in horsepower,</b></font>

232
00:13:39,224 --> 00:13:42,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the FD is the best
domestic cornering machine.</b></font>

233
00:13:42,864 --> 00:13:45,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both in the straights and in the turns,</b></font>

234
00:13:45,104 --> 00:13:47,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the Eight-Six is outclassed!</b></font>

235
00:13:47,804 --> 00:13:50,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We just need to have faith in him...</b></font>

236
00:13:58,644 --> 00:14:00,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then we'll begin the countdown.</b></font>

237
00:14:00,414 --> 00:14:03,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Roger!
--Roger!</b></font>

238
00:14:03,254 --> 00:14:06,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ten seconds to green!</b></font>

239
00:14:06,324 --> 00:14:08,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nine! Eight!</b></font>

240
00:14:08,524 --> 00:14:11,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seven! Six!</b></font>

241
00:14:11,024 --> 00:14:14,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five! Four! Three!</b></font>

242
00:14:14,694 --> 00:14:17,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two! One!</b></font>

243
00:14:17,034 --> 00:14:18,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

244
00:14:43,254 --> 00:14:46,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fast! Keisuke Takahashi's FD!</b></font>

245
00:14:46,464 --> 00:14:48,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>350 horses are no joke.</b></font>

246
00:14:48,864 --> 00:14:50,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His shifting is perfect.</b></font>

247
00:14:50,434 --> 00:14:51,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no match.</b></font>

248
00:14:51,964 --> 00:14:57,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At full acceleration, the Eight-Six
looked like it was standing still.</b></font>

249
00:14:57,404 --> 00:15:00,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

250
00:15:00,704 --> 00:15:07,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Coming off the line, that Eight-Six</i>
<i>has 150 horsepower at most.</i></b></font>

251
00:15:07,414 --> 00:15:11,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's not quite the monster</i>
<i>Keisuke was talking about.</i></b></font>

252
00:15:11,524 --> 00:15:13,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The reason why it can shift so fast</i></b></font>

253
00:15:13,154 --> 00:15:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is that it has tranny gears for a rally.</i></b></font>

254
00:15:15,994 --> 00:15:20,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It must be perfect for the hairpins on Akina.</i></b></font>

255
00:15:20,324 --> 00:15:21,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still, there's no reason</i></b></font>

256
00:15:21,594 --> 00:15:26,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Keisuke's FD would be beat out by it.</i></b></font>

257
00:15:26,434 --> 00:15:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The monster isn't the car...</i></b></font>

258
00:15:29,534 --> 00:15:31,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but the driver?!</i></b></font>

259
00:15:39,044 --> 00:15:40,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't give him a break.</i></b></font>

260
00:15:40,784 --> 00:15:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't like using the</i>
<i>straightaways to pull ahead,</i></b></font>

261
00:15:43,054 --> 00:15:45,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but this is a timed run.</i></b></font>

262
00:15:45,554 --> 00:15:49,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll never even see that</i>
<i>Eight-Six in my rearview mirror.</i></b></font>

263
00:16:28,234 --> 00:16:29,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?!</b></font>

264
00:16:29,334 --> 00:16:32,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the first corner! It's great!
The Eight-Six's line is incredible!</b></font>

265
00:16:32,564 --> 00:16:35,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wasn't more than 5 cm from the guardrail!</b></font>

266
00:16:35,334 --> 00:16:38,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen anyone corner at that speed!</b></font>

267
00:16:52,384 --> 00:16:54,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

268
00:16:54,124 --> 00:16:55,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's closing the gap?!</i></b></font>

269
00:16:55,594 --> 00:16:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's getting closer?!</i></b></font>

270
00:17:00,124 --> 00:17:01,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It must be my imagination!</i></b></font>

271
00:17:01,334 --> 00:17:03,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's impossible!</i></b></font>

272
00:17:51,284 --> 00:17:53,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are... Are you serious?!</b></font>

273
00:17:53,184 --> 00:17:56,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's father was once a great street racer?</b></font>

274
00:17:56,954 --> 00:17:58,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

275
00:17:58,384 --> 00:18:01,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've seen him several times,</b></font>

276
00:18:01,224 --> 00:18:04,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he's just the gruff owner of the tofu shop.</b></font>

277
00:18:04,194 --> 00:18:07,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess you really can't tell much
about a person by just looking at them.</b></font>

278
00:18:07,124 --> 00:18:11,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>According to Mr. Tachibana, he's still
the fastest on the downhill in Akina.</b></font>

279
00:18:12,534 --> 00:18:17,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, that's who sent Takumi in his place,</b></font>

280
00:18:17,504 --> 00:18:19,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so we should just believe in Takumi.</b></font>

281
00:18:19,344 --> 00:18:22,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah... It's much better than if I had run.</b></font>

282
00:18:22,244 --> 00:18:26,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But even if his father is fast, Takumi is...</b></font>

283
00:18:26,644 --> 00:18:31,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like Takumi beat
Keisuke Takahashi once before.</b></font>

284
00:18:31,354 --> 00:18:32,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

285
00:18:32,554 --> 00:18:37,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi defeated Keisuke Takahashi?! No way!</b></font>

286
00:18:39,364 --> 00:18:42,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe it! That spacey Takumi?!</b></font>

287
00:18:42,834 --> 00:18:46,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He didn't even know what an Eight-Six was!</b></font>

288
00:19:00,214 --> 00:19:02,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! What's in that Eight-Six?!</b></font>

289
00:19:02,554 --> 00:19:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At incredible speed, it came
in with the rear end free</b></font>

290
00:19:05,184 --> 00:19:08,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and it passed through
at an unbelievable speed!</b></font>

291
00:19:08,154 --> 00:19:09,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wouldn't be surprising if it
went airborne at any moment!</b></font>

292
00:19:09,794 --> 00:19:11,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've got shivers going up our spines!</b></font>

293
00:19:25,204 --> 00:19:26,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's caught up to me?!</i></b></font>

294
00:19:26,704 --> 00:19:30,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's happening? I must be going crazy!</i></b></font>

295
00:20:00,344 --> 00:20:02,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up to second gear, they're the same,</b></font>

296
00:20:02,574 --> 00:20:04,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but the stretch is different...</b></font>

297
00:20:04,544 --> 00:20:07,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the straight is even a
little long, he'll pull away...</b></font>

298
00:20:19,194 --> 00:20:21,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the straightaway
in front of the skating rink.</b></font>

299
00:20:21,094 --> 00:20:22,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The two of them just passed by!</b></font>

300
00:20:22,794 --> 00:20:24,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's on Keisuke's bumper!</b></font>

301
00:20:24,764 --> 00:20:27,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six is unbelievably fast!</b></font>

302
00:20:27,434 --> 00:20:28,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this for real?!</b></font>

303
00:20:28,734 --> 00:20:33,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's FD has never had
anyone keep up with it this far!</b></font>

304
00:20:36,744 --> 00:20:39,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, I've got goosebumps...</b></font>

305
00:20:39,784 --> 00:20:42,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On this long straightaway,
Keisuke pulled away,</b></font>

306
00:20:42,284 --> 00:20:46,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but after this, there are many
hairpins. It may be a problem!</b></font>

307
00:20:46,824 --> 00:20:48,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you hear him, Ryosuke?</b></font>

308
00:20:48,424 --> 00:20:50,454
